					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12050234#post-4274622</guid>
				<title>The janitor strikes back.</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12050234/scp-4557#post-4274622</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2019 00:49:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>JanitorCakeworth</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3484414</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p><em>You ding dongs thought I was gone, didn't you?</em></p> <p>Eh, so did I. But I felt that Detective Fiver should have at least gotten the spotlight. Plus, I was continuously bored and decided to take on this project for real this time.</p> <p>This may or may not mark the restart of my SCP career. I advise you don't hold your breath, but do stay tuned if you so desire.</p> <p>First image was taken by Hobvias Sudoneighm. <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/striatic/20181712">Here is the link I took it from.</a></p> <p>Second image was taken by Investigatio. (Cool name.) <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Odesa_Artillery_school_Apartment_building_1-2.jpg">Here is the link I took it from.</a></p> <p>The third image was constructed by yours truly.</p> <p>Many thanks to everyone who peeped at this SCP in its early stages. Even in its <em>very</em> early stages.</p> <p>Love you all.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
